\\\\\\n`[25]` Human time perception and its illusions: *https\\\\://www\\\\.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2866156/*\\\\\\n`[26]` 波动: *https\\\\://medium.com/mycrypto/the-history-of-ethereum-hard-forks-6a6dae76d56f*\\\\\\n`[27]` 12秒区块时间: *https\\\\://consensys.net/blog/blockchain-explained/charting-the-path-to-proof-of-stake-ethereum/*\\\\\\n`[28]` 小博客文章: *https\\\\://prestwi.ch/we-are-the-watchmaker-gods-now/*\\\\\\n`[29]` 以太坊的难度调整: *https\\\\://tjayrush.medium.com/its-not-that-difficult-33a428c3c2c3*\\n\",\"timestamp\":1638914786,\"title\":\"以太时钟：一个高斯计时器\"},\"digest\":\"IKYHS6BGXB0prR_QA5NyKm92YKBp4zrrZHq7hqtgHPY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8A155c86b7bcc256bbacF813aDa1cfBE60d71AD3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7mfsvbfSg1U9ZldOabH8EmMy5XIAXfwTEaVLydFksAU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Aj4BJA2T2LAFJKLj_hvsVimAabuGq7Wnjech8vSnx8M\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hzW3j7Y5fSIKtnZnSvUaig3YC2Jul2gi21-1veBICnHUHFji0SwzLfSiOJIq3oF8I3gAnrL27BhuWQS8rugyIg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3771003a4e92e9bd384e9f26dd4262f168d1d9285783d6e5bfb7fefc98a64bb51c718074920350af57410678ee63b59a5bb8072e7473fd26403fe757a37fb9e11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7mfsvbfSg1U9ZldOabH8EmMy5XIAXfwTEaVLydFksAU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Aj4BJA2T2LAFJKLj_hvsVimAabuGq7Wnjech8vSnx8M\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"IKYHS6BGXB0prR_QA5NyKm92YKBp4zrrZHq7hqtgHPY\"}"